2. You need an [audio][2] tag in order to play sound.
3. You can trigger [play()][3] using the event registered on step 1
4. Add an [ended][4] event to the audio tag to know when the audio ended
5. Use [location.href][5] to navigate to another URL

You can hide the audio player if you want using styles.

